#: src/Admin/Settings.php:98
msgid "Controls whether the registry feature appears to customers and guests. Both options are on by default, so registries work the moment the plugin is active, no setup required."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:102
msgid "Enable gift registries"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/Settings.php:108
msgid "Show gift registries on the storefront."
